<plot>Nancy Barrett, one of the stars of the cult classic TV show Dark Shadows returns to several locations used for exterior shots on the show. Among the places visited: Seaview Terrace, the mansion that "played" Collinwood and the Black Pearl restaurant, which doubled for the Blue Whale bar.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?127331</url></doc>
